dc_title_s: Map of the states of Ohio, Indiana and Illinois with the settled part of Michigan; engraved by J. H. Young.; Title on cover: Mitchell's map of Ohio, Indiana, Illinois & Michigan MiU
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. Prime meridian: Washington. "Sold by Mitchell & Hinman." Insets: Vicinity of Detroit -- Vicinity of Cincinnati -- Falls of Ohio -- Lead region east of the Mississippi River. Includes table of steamboat routes. 1 map: hand col.; 42 x 54 cm
